       The tech specs
       line illustration of the Fairphone 3

Operating system
       Android 9

Performance
       Qualcomm Snapdragon 632
       4GB RAM
          + 64-bit Octa-Core processor
          + Processor speed up to 1.8GHz
          + Qualcomm Adreno 506 650MHz GPU

Storage
       64GB internal storage
       Expandable with a microSD card
          + External storage: microSD

Battery
       3,000mAH removable Li-ion battery
          + 3060 mAH typical capacity
          + 300 hours whilst idle
          + 20 hours with phone calls
          + 3.5 hour charging time

Display
       5.65 inch Full HD+ 18:9
          + LCD (IPS) touchscreen
          + 18:9 aspect ratio
          + 2160 x 1080 resolution
          + 427ppi pixel density
          + Gorilla Glass 5
          + No. of colors: 16 million

Cameras
       12MP rear camera • f/1.8 • Dual Pixel PDAF
       8MP front camera • f/2.0

Rear camera
          + 12MP resolution with HDR
          + 1/2.55" sensor
          + f1.8 aperture
          + Autofocus + phase detection
          + IMX363 sensor
          + Digital Image Stabilization
          + Dual LED flash
          + Up to 8x digitial zoom
          + Max video resolution 3840 x 2160
          + 4K video @ 30fps
          + 1080p @ 30fps
          + 720p @ 60fps

Front camera
          + 8MP resolution with HDR
          + 1/4" sensor
          + f2.0 aperture
          + Digital Image Stabilization
          + Up to 8x digital zoom

Wireless & location
       2.4 & 5 GHz WiFi • Bluetooth® 5 + LE
       NFC for card payments & more
          + WiFi support 802.11 a/b/g/n/ac
          + WiFi direct support
          + GNSS standards: GPS, Glonass, Galileo
          + A-GPS support

Network
       Dual Nano SIM
       4G (LTE)
          + Nano SIM (4FF)
          + Max SAR head (W/kg @ 10g) = 0.388
          + Max SAR body (W/kg @ 10g) = 1.405

4G (LTE)
          + Type - Cat. 13
          + MIMO - 4x2
          + 2CA Carrier Aggregation
          + VoLTE + VoWiFi
          + Bands - 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 7, 8, 13, 20, 26
          + Max download speed 300Mbps
          + Max upload speed 150Mbps

3G (HSPA+)
          + HSDPA - Cat 24
          + HSUPA - Cat 6
          + Frequencies - 800, 850, 900, 1700, 1900, 2100 Mhz
          + Max download speed 42Mbps
          + Max upload speed 5.76Mbps

2G (GMS, GPRS, EDGE)
          + Type - Cat. 33
          + Frequencies - 850, 900, 1800, 1900 Mhz

Connectors & sensors
       USB Type - C
       Fingerprint scanner
          + USB 2.0 support
          + Ambient Light
          + Accelerometer
          + Gyroscope
          + Proximity
          + Barometer
          + Compass

Media & audio
       3.5mm Headphone jack
          + External speaker loudness: 95db @ 10cm
          + Miracast support

Supported video codecs
          + HEVC, H.264, VC-1, MPEG-4, DivX, MPEG-2, H.263, VP8, VP9

Supported audio codecs
          + PCM playback, AAC/AAC+/eAAC+, MP3, WMA (v9, v10), WMALossless,
            WMAPro 10, AMR-NB, AMR-WB, FLAC, ALAC, Vorbis, AIFF, APE

Design
       Dark Translucent body and cover
          + Length 158 mm
          + Width 71.8 mm
          + Thickness 9.89 mm
          + Weight: 189g
       Fairphone 3 packaging
       In the box If you don’t need it, we don’t include it! There’s no
       charger, cable or earphones, so you can use the ones you have and
       help cut down on e-waste.

           Included:    Not included:
       Fairphone 3      USB-C cable
       Mini screwdriver Charger
