       Shipping & returns
       How long does delivery take and what does it cost?
       Once shipped, delivery will take between 2-10 working days,
       depending on your country and shipping address. The shipping costs
       all depend on your country and shipping address and will be stated
       on the checkout page, after you’ve selected your country and
       shipping address.
       How long do I have to return the phone?
       You have 14 days after the delivery date to let us know that you
       want to return the phone. More info
       Will I receive a Track & Trace link?
       Yes, you will receive a Trace & Trace link within 24 hours of your
       Fairphone 3 being shipped.
       When will I get my pre-ordered phone?
       Shipping starts early October. Once shipped, we will send you a
       shipping confirmation email within 24 hours, including a link to
       Track & Trace your delivery. More info
       Together we can change the way products are made
