       Specifiche tecniche
       line illustration of the Fairphone 3

Sistema Operativo
       Android 9

Processore
       Qualcomm Snapdragon 632
       4GB RAM
          + 64-bit Octa-Core processor
          + Processor speed up to 1.8GHz
          + Qualcomm Adreno 506 650MHz GPU

Memoria ROM
       64GB di memoria interna
       Espandibile con una scheda MicroSD
          + External storage: microSD

Batteria
       Li-ion rimovibile, da 3000 mAh
          + 3060 mAH typical capacity
          + 300 hours whilst idle
          + 20 hours with phone calls
          + 3.5 hour charging time

Schermo
       5,65 pollici Full HD+ 18:9
          + LCD (IPS) touchscreen
          + 18:9 aspect ratio
          + 2160 x 1080 resolution
          + 427ppi pixel density
          + Gorilla Glass 5
          + No. of colors: 16 million

Fotocamera
       Fotocamera posteriore da 12 MP • f/1.8 • Dual Pixel PDAF
       Fotocamera anteriore da 8 MP • f/2.0

Fotocamera posteriore
          + 12MP risoluzione, supporto HDR
          + 1/2.55" sensore
          + f1.8 apertura
          + Autofocus + PDAF
          + IMX363 sensore
          + Stabilizzazione digitale dell'immagine
          + Doppio LED flash
          + Fino a 8x zoom digitiale
          + Massima risoluzione video supportata in registrazione 3840 x
            2160
          + 4K video a 30fps
          + 1080p a 30fps
          + 720p a 60fps

Fotocamera anteriore
          + 8MP risoluzione, supporto HDR
          + 1/4" sensore
          + f2.0 Apertura
          + Stabilizzazione digitale dell'immagine
          + Zoom digitale fino a 8x

Wireless
       2.4 & 5 GHz WiFi • Bluetooth® 5 + LE
       NFC
          + WiFi support 802.11 a/b/g/n/ac
          + WiFi direct support
          + GNSS standards: GPS, Glonass, Galileo
          + A-GPS support

Rete
       Dual Nano SIM
       4G (LTE)
          + Nano SIM (4FF)
          + Max SAR head (W/kg @ 10g) = 0.388
          + Max SAR body (W/kg @ 10g) = 1.405

4G (LTE)
          + Type - Cat. 13
          + MIMO - 4x2
          + 2CA Carrier Aggregation
          + VoLTE + VoWiFi
          + Bands - 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 7, 8, 13, 20, 26
          + Max download speed 300Mbps
          + Max upload speed 150Mbps

3G (HSPA+)
          + HSDPA - Cat 24
          + HSUPA - Cat 6
          + Frequencies - 800, 850, 900, 1700, 1900, 2100 Mhz
          + Max download speed 42Mbps
          + Max upload speed 5.76Mbps

2G (GMS, GPRS, EDGE)
          + Type - Cat. 33
          + Frequencies - 850, 900, 1800, 1900 Mhz

Connettori e Sensori
       USB Tipo - C
       Scanner impronta digitale
          + USB 2.0 support
          + Ambient Light
          + Accelerometer
          + Gyroscope
          + Proximity
          + Barometer
          + Compass

Media & audio
       3.5mm Jack cuffie
          + External speaker loudness: 95db @ 10cm
          + Miracast support

Supported video codecs
          + HEVC, H.264, VC-1, MPEG-4, DivX, MPEG-2, H.263, VP8, VP9

Supported audio codecs
          + PCM playback, AAC/AAC+/eAAC+, MP3, WMA (v9, v10), WMALossless,
            WMAPro 10, AMR-NB, AMR-WB, FLAC, ALAC, Vorbis, AIFF, APE

Design
       Dark Translucent body and cover
          + Length 158 mm
          + Width 71.8 mm
          + Thickness 9.89 mm
          + Weight: 189g
